after buying it should not be interpreted as value consensus, and vice versa.

The concept of value consensus and earnings consensus is a bit like the concept of investment and speculation, we must ensure that the logic before and after the investment is consistent, if the underlying is earnings consensus,
once the subject's profit path is tested, the earnings consensus will be directly impacted, and if the volume is too small, it may be scattered at any time.
On the contrary, the earnings consensus is more short-term, meaning that people want to make money on a certain subject in a certain cycle,
value consensus will be difficult to be penetrated in the short term, which is one of the main reasons why I am bullish on LUNA in the long term.

A company or organization, through its unique business model to intervene in a market and gain its own competitiveness, so as to solve the problems in life after gaining the support of users, investors, I call this situation value consensus. Once formed,
Warren Buffett and Munger's concept of value investing has explained very well what value consensus is.
while some consensus is strong and not easily broken, and some consensus is fragile and easily destroyed, and it will be different at different stages of the development of things.

This explanation does make sense, but we need to understand that consensus can be divided into many kinds, both the value consensus that agrees with the application value of the project and the profit consensus that generally believes that the underlying will rise,

What is consensus? Many people always mention the word consensus when analyzing the reason for the rise of a coin with a huge increase. What they mean is that the holders/community have a consensus that has led to a low selling pressure and the ability to keep rising.
